descriptionHtml:
YES another Megan Fox:D
She is in Riverwood but havent done any quests yet. Went with Imperials. Screnshots have been taken with Sharpshooters ENB so might look different without it or with any other ENB\\\'s. Higly recommended using sharpshooters ENB or some else.

Needed Mods: 
Temptress Race: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18717

	
RaceCompatibility http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24168


ApachiiSkyHair: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168/

this will be needed also but not necessary(she still look like in picture but minor changes without this)Enchanted character edit:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12951

An yet she dont look as the picture? try this also:BFG - Better FaceGen:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6953

I have dawnguard and heartfire DLC\'s. But dont think those are required anyways:) Just let you know!:P

recommended ENB!! (or might look same with other ENB also) havent try.
(with this you get the same look on colours and lights etc.)
sharpshooters ENB: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15105

I tested this save only these mods on and she looked just like in picture. So comment if she still aint looking the same. And post a picture that i could see what it might miss. Hope this helps! 



Hope youll like her.
